  "text": "We used the same set of 29 096 individuals with CD and 144 522 controls matched for age, gender and calendar period as in our previous study on mortality in CD. [CITATION_1] Sixteen per cent of CD patients were diagnosed <2 years of age (table 1) . Most study participants were female (62%), and the majority were diagnosed after year 1990.",
